{"title":"夜的山花","authors":["杨山"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":3,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜的山花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山中有雾，雾中有花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬崖近，星花开了，照亮夜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山路上，车的队列轰隆隆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯在星中驰，星里人出发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁在炼钢炉前，以钢钎作笔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绘千朵万朵钢的花蕾？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁在织布机旁，以春的柔情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谱春的旋律，织春的奇葩？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高楼里，计算机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在运算美，星在窗前笑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江上是星，是灯？在浪中闪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜航船拖一弯新月，远走天涯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必徘徊。有灯引路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失落的是寂寞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必惆怅。有星作伴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山上山下开遍夜的山花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远方的来客，请摘一朵带回家。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}